 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20090413164902/http://lwn.net/Articles/216456/
 |dead-url     = no
}}</ref>，並且是在[[GNU通用公共许可证|GNU 通用公共授權條款]]下發布的[[自由軟體|自由軟體]]。<ref>{{cite web
 |url          = http://www.linuxlinks.com/article/20080407161916432/Konversation.html
